---
title: Zesty One-Pot Chili  with Cheesy Tortilla Chips
description: This quick and zesty beef chili, simmered with black beans, packs a major flavour punch in just 15 minutes. Enjoy it with crispy, cheesy tortilla chips for dipping.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1049_W33_CA_RB27774-1_Mainlow-b323edb7.jpg
